        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">domains</ENAMEX> assessed by the NPI-<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Q. Anxiety</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">depression</ENAMEX>,
