        behavioral problem was highly correlated with the distress
        to <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">staff</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">rho</ENAMEX> =<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">.70</NUMEX>; p <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">< .001</NUMEX>). <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Table 2</ENAMEX>. lists the mean
        severity and mean level of distress to staff for each
